title: Grand Theft Auto V (GTA V) All crash fix (Including TIEUP-0014)
description:
This patch has been taken a lot of work to create. There's no bullsh*t. No malware or anything. This is the pure fix for Each and every single crash in gta v. 

NOTE - THIS ONLY WORKS FOR THE GAME VERSION 1.0.350.1
NOTE - THIS IS NOT ILLEGAL. THIS IS JUST A FIX FOR ERRORS

If you don't trust, upload anywhere and check for malware first.

1. Get the update V4 (1.0.350.1) and install

2. Get this fix and copy everything to the Game Directory

3. Launch the game with Fix_Launcher.exe

4. Enjoy crash free GTA V.


Video Tut - www(dot)youtube(dot)com/watch?v=9tGLYWbYKUg


Please buy the original version of the game and Support Rockstar Games. They've done a hell of a job :)
